                <ul class="space-y-2 text-light-700 dark:text-dark-300 font-mono text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">-</span>
                    <span>Deep AI research across blogs, reviews, and local guides</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">-</span>
                    <span>Smart itineraries with day-by-day pacing and booking links</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                    <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">-</span>
                    <span>Hidden gems and local insights tailored to preferences</span>
                  </li>
