                  <p><span class="text-code-400">Frontend:</span> Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind</p>
                  <p><span class="text-terminal-400">Backend:</span> FastAPI + CrewAI multi-agent system</p>
                  <p><span class="text-primary-400">Data:</span> Postgres (Supabase) + Drizzle ORM</p>
                  <p><span class="text-light-700 dark:text-dark-300">Infra:</span> Better Auth, Upstash, AWS S3/SES</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex space-x-4 pt-4">
